message.content: {"description":"Get hourly swap volume statistics aggregated from Uniswap V3 pool swaps.","endpoint_path":"/api/v3/volume/hourly","method":"GET","path_params":[],"query_params":[{"default":50,"name":"limit","type":"u32"},{"default":"null","name":"startBlockTimestamp","type":"Option<u64>"},{"default":"null","name":"endBlockTimestamp","type":"Option<u64>"}],"response_schema":{"fields":[{"description":"Hour timestamp for the aggregated data","name":"hour","type":"i64"},{"description":"Total number of swaps in the hour","name":"swap_count","type":"i64"},{"description":"Total amount0 swapped in the hour","name":"total_amount0","type":"String"},{"description":"Total amount1 swapped in the hour","name":"total_amount1","type":"String"}],"name":"HourlyVolumeResponse"},"sql_query":"SELECT DATE_TRUNC('hour', TO_TIMESTAMP(block_timestamp)) AS hour, COUNT(*) AS swap_count, SUM(amount0) AS total_amount0, SUM(amount1) AS total_amount1 FROM v3_pool_swaps WHERE ($1::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp >= $1) AND ($2::BIGINT IS NULL OR block_timestamp <= $2) GROUP BY hour ORDER BY hour DESC LIMIT $3","tables_referenced":["v3_pool_swaps"]}
